=== Access ===
* 20 minutes by car from {{ill|lt=Yamato Interchange|Q10934247|qid=Q10934247|1=Taiwa interchange}} on the {{ill|lt=Tōhoku Expressway|Q428428|qid=Q428428|1=Tōhoku Expressway}}
* 10 minutes by car from {{ill|lt=Tomiya Interchange|Q16144881|qid=Q16144881|1=Tomiya interchange}} on the {{ill|lt=Sendai Hokubu Road|Q11377788|qid=Q11377788|1=Sendai-Hokubu Road}}
* 20 minutes by car from {{ill|lt=Izumi Interchange|Q11143029|qid=Q11143029|1=Izumi interchange}} on the {{ill|lt=Tōhoku Expressway|Q428428|qid=Q428428|1=Tōhoku Expressway}}

